PARMELE PHARMACAL CO., Plaintiff-Appellant, v. Louis I. WEINER, Trading as the Tablax Co., Defendant-Appellee. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. January 19, 1925.) No. 145. Prindle, Wright, Neal & Bean, of New York City, for appellant. Walter H. Pumphrey, of New York City, for appellee.

Before ROGERS, HOUGH, and HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree 5 F.(2d) 750, affirmed.
